			<<link [[당신을 가린다 (0:15)|Monster Tower Cover]]>><<pass 15>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[짐승을 안정시킨다 (1:00)|Monster Tower Calm]]>><<pass 60>><<set $tower_sleep to 115>><</link>>
